title: Flying Girls Return in Strike Witches: 501st JOINT FIGHTER WING Take Off! Movie Edition Key Visual & Trailer
description: The official website for the anime adaptation project based on Makoto Fujibayashi's spin-off gag manga Strike Witches: 501st JOINT FIGHTER WING Take Off! has posted a key visual and a 50-second trailer for its forthcoming 30-minute special episode that will get a theatrical run in Japan from October 4, 2019. Meet the cute witches again after the jump!
